<h2 style="color:#18181b; font-size:22px; font-weight:700; margin:0 0 16px;">You're subscribed.</h2>

<p style="color:#52525b; font-size:15px; margin:0 0 16px;">
  Hey <%= @user.first_name.presence || @user.username %> —
</p>

<p style="color:#52525b; font-size:15px; margin:0 0 24px;">
  Your subscription to Train Like Dubi is active. You now have full access to Mauricio's training library — every video, every drill, every rep.
</p>

<div style="background-color:#f0fdf4; border:1px solid #bbf7d0; border-radius:8px; padding:16px 20px; margin:0 0 24px;">
  <p style="color:#166534; font-size:14px; font-weight:600; margin:0 0 4px;">Subscription active</p>
  <p style="color:#166534; font-size:14px; margin:0;">
    Next billing date: <strong><%= @subscription.current_period_end&.strftime("%B %-d, %Y") %></strong>
  </p>
</div>

<p style="text-align:center; margin:0 0 28px;">
  <%= link_to "Start Watching",
      videos_url,
      style: "display:inline-block; padding:14px 32px; background-color:#dc2626; color:#ffffff; text-decoration:none; border-radius:8px; font-weight:700; font-size:15px;" %>
</p>

<hr style="border:none; border-top:1px solid #e4e4e7; margin:0 0 20px;">

<p style="color:#71717a; font-size:13px; margin:0;">
  Questions about your subscription? Reply to this email or reach us at
  <a href="mailto:support@trainlikedubi.com" style="color:#ef4444; text-decoration:none;">support@trainlikedubi.com</a>.
</p>
